  "body": "**Issue Template**\r\n\r\n*Title*: *Upgrading __yapf__ in __tools/requirements.txt__ breaks the build.*\r\n\r\n*Description*:\r\n\r\nMost projects are moving quickly to [__python/black__](https://github.com/python/black) but we can stick with yapf if we want.  However, we have [__yapf==0.25.0__ hardcoded in __tools/requirements.txt__](https://github.com/envoyproxy/envoy/blob/master/tools/requirements.txt#L2) and when we upgrade to the [current version (0.27.0)](https://pypi.org/project/yapf), our build fails.\r\n* https://github.com/google/yapf/blob/master/CHANGELOG",
